Package CS509.client.airplane

Class Airplane

java.lang.Object
CS509.client.airplane.Airplane
public class Airplane extends Object
This class stores information about an airplane. This class presents the same information as received from the CS509 server after conversion from XML strings to java primitives. Each data attribute is accessible via getters and setters
Since:
2016-02-24
Version:
1.1
Author:
blake
